<div class="col-md-6">
  <h2>Sign up</h2>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
  <h2>Why register for Antisocial?</h2>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6">
  <%= simple_form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>

    <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.input :first_name, :autofocus => true, required: false, input_html: { class: "form-control" }, error_html: { style: "color: red" } %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.input :last_name, required: false, input_html: { class: "form-control" }, error_html: { style: "color: red" } %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.input :profile_name, required: false, input_html: { class: "form-control" }, error_html: { style: "color: red" } %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.input :email, required: false, input_html: { class: "form-control" }, error_html: { style: "color: red" } %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.input :password, required: false, input_html: { class: "form-control" }, error_html: { style: "color: red" } %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.input :password_confirmation, required: false, input_html: { class: "form-control" }, error_html: { style: "color: red" } %>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 20px 0 15px 0">
      <%= f.submit "Sign up", class: "btn btn-success" %>
    </div>

  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6">
  <p>You've seen all those other social networks - Facebook, Twitter, App.net, etc. They're all good. Why should you sign up for yet another?</p>

  <br>

  <h4>Reason Number One</h4>
    <p>Do you know of any social networks named "Antisocial"? That's so ironic and awesome!</p> 

  <br>

  <h4>Reason Number Two</h4>
    <p>There are two different kinds of social networks -- The micro-blogging Twitter-style kind and the friending/status-updating Facebook-style kind. Antisocial aims to combine those two ways into one, awesome site.</p>

  <br>

  <h4>Reason Number Three</h4>
    <p>It would make the developer really happy, and it's free. Don't you want to make a developer happy?</p>

  <br>

  <h4>Still Not Convinced?</h4>
    <p>Okay, fine. Don't sign up then, you grumpy pants.</p>

  <br>

  <h4>Are You Still Reading?</h4>
    <p>If so, congrats. You made it to the end. Now fill out that form!</p>
</div>